Universal Hospital Services Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















universal hospital services inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Health Care
Industry: Health Care Facilities & Svcs
Sub-Industry: Health Care Supply Chain
Universal Hospital Services, Inc. provides medical equipment. The Company offers bariatrics, beds, pulmonary therapy mattresses, fall prevention, ventilators, breast pumps, patient monitoring, chairs, and surgical equipment as well as grants clinical engineering, on-site management, and surgical services. Universal Hospital Services serves hospitals in the United States.




