UHS | Better Equipped to Care™






Better Equipped to Care™

Patient care is your top priority—ours, too. UHS can provide, manage and maintain medical equipment throughout your facility, ensuring you always have the right tools at the right time, with more time to give your patients the attention and care they deserve.












 Let’s think big picture

The evolving health care environment requires a deeper understanding of how the medical equipment you use impacts your quality of care. Discover how an end-to-end approach to medical equipment management can increase value to your organization. 





































Access
Quality equipmentyou can trust







Manage
Medical equipment efficiently







Maintain
Equipment to maximize performance














Get the equipmentyou need
Addressing equipment demand for emergent patient needs requires a strategic approach. Let’s talk about how accessing patient-ready equipment can positively impact your patient care.






Learn More















Equipment when and where it’s needed
Rapid equipment turn-around plays a pivotal role in patient care. Let’s discuss how to optimize your on-site equipment throughput to ensure that caregivers have access to the right equipment, when and where they need it.






Learn More















Ensure quality and regulatory standards
Service cost management, equipment uptime and regulatory compliance. Individually, these goals are hard to achieve. Let’s discuss how a coordinated service management strategy can help you realize these goals while maintaining quality to the highest industry standards.






Learn More










