About UHS






About UHS

Universal Hospital Services (UHS) is a clinical equipment services company that helps health care organizations increase operating efficiencies by optimizing the equipment lifecycle. We help you access, manage and maintain medical equipment so that your clinical staff is better equipped to care ™ for patients. 












What We Do





We Manage
700,000+
Pieces of medical equipment






We work with
7,000+
Acute care hospitals & alternate site providers






We have
80+
District Service Centers throughout the U.S.






We've spent the last
75+
Years proudly serving the healthcare industry



















Through equipment management solutions, world-class service, and decades of experience.
UHS makes you better equipped to care.™



We can provide you with
Medical Equipment Rental
Get 24/7 access to the medical and surgical equipment you need, when you need it. 

Rent Now


We can provide you with
Medical Equipment Services
Discover smarter ways to manage and maintain your medical equipment – clinical engineering, on-site managed programs, and surgical services – so that you can focus on patient care. 

Learn More














